flowchart TD
    Start([CLI Entry: main.py]) --> ArgParse[Parse Arguments<br/>--decode, --output<br/>--refresh-mitre<br/>--batch-input<br/>--generate-report]
    ArgParse --> BatchCheck{--batch-input flag?}
    
    BatchCheck -->|Yes| BatchPath[Load Batch Commands<br/>batch_processor.py<br/>JSON/CSV/TXT parsing]
    BatchPath --> ProcessBatch[process_batch_commands<br/>Loop through all commands]
    ProcessBatch --> BatchPipeline
    
    BatchCheck -->|No| ReadInput{Input Source?}
    ReadInput -->|Arguments| JoinArgs[Join command args]
    ReadInput -->|stdin| ReadStdin[Read from stdin]
    JoinArgs --> SinglePipeline
    ReadStdin --> SinglePipeline
    
    SinglePipeline[translate_command<br/>pipeline.py<br/>Single command] --> DecodeCheck{--decode flag?}
    BatchPipeline[Analyze each command<br/>via translate_command] --> DecodeCheck
    
    DecodeCheck -->|Yes| DetectEnc[detect_encoding_types<br/>decoder.py]
    DetectEnc --> DecodeCmd[decode_command<br/>decoder.py]
    DecodeCmd --> DecodeResult{Decoded?}
    DecodeResult -->|Yes| UseDecoded[Use decoded command<br/>Store decode_info]
    DecodeResult -->|No| UseOriginal1[Use original command]
    DecodeCheck -->|No| UseOriginal2[Use original command]
    
    UseDecoded --> Normalize
    UseOriginal1 --> Normalize
    UseOriginal2 --> Normalize
    
    Normalize[normalize_command<br/>parser.py] --> GetCache[get_attackcti_cache<br/>mitre.py]
    
    GetCache --> DetectAll[Detect ALL 7 Techniques<br/>Always enabled by default]
    DetectAll --> DetectT1059[detect_t1059<br/>Command & Scripting]
    DetectT1059 --> MatchIndicators1[_match_indicators]
    MatchIndicators1 --> ScoreConf1[score_confidence]
    
    ScoreConf1 --> DetectT1218[detect_t1218<br/>LOLBins detection]
    DetectT1218 --> MatchIndicators2[_match_indicators]
    MatchIndicators2 --> ScoreConf2[score_confidence]
    
    ScoreConf2 --> DetectT1027[detect_t1027<br/>Obfuscation detection]
    DetectT1027 --> MatchIndicators3[_match_indicators]
    MatchIndicators3 --> ScoreConf3[score_confidence]
    
    ScoreConf3 --> DetectT1105[detect_t1105<br/>Ingress Tool Transfer]
    DetectT1105 --> MatchIndicators4[_match_indicators]
    MatchIndicators4 --> ScoreConf4[score_confidence]
    
    ScoreConf4 --> DetectT1071[detect_t1071<br/>Application Layer Protocol]
    DetectT1071 --> MatchIndicators5[_match_indicators]
    MatchIndicators5 --> ScoreConf5[score_confidence]
    
    ScoreConf5 --> DetectT1543[detect_t1543<br/>Persistence detection]
    DetectT1543 --> MatchIndicators6[_match_indicators]
    MatchIndicators6 --> ScoreConf6[score_confidence]
    
    ScoreConf6 --> DetectT1055[detect_t1055<br/>Process Injection]
    DetectT1055 --> MatchIndicators7[_match_indicators]
    MatchIndicators7 --> ScoreConf7[score_confidence]
    
    ScoreConf7 --> MergeDetections[Merge all 7 technique<br/>detections]
    
    MergeDetections --> BuildOutput[build_output<br/>output.py]
    BuildOutput --> EnrichDet[_enrich_detections<br/>Add metadata from METADATA_DB]
    EnrichDet --> DedupeEv[_dedupe_evidence]
    DedupeEv --> AddDecodeInfo{decode_info<br/>available?}
    
    AddDecodeInfo -->|Yes| AddDecodeMeta[Add decode_info to output]
    AddDecodeInfo -->|No| CheckBatch
    AddDecodeMeta --> CheckBatch
    
    CheckBatch{Batch or<br/>Single?}
    CheckBatch -->|Single| FinalOutput[Final JSON Output]
    CheckBatch -->|Batch| AggregateResults[Aggregate batch results<br/>& metadata]
    
    AggregateResults --> BatchOutput[Batch JSON Output]
    
    FinalOutput --> ReportCheck{--generate-report?}
    BatchOutput --> ReportCheck
    
    ReportCheck -->|Yes| GenReport[generate_report<br/>report_generator.py<br/>Create HTML visualization]
    ReportCheck -->|No| OutputCheck
    GenReport --> SaveReport[Save HTML to<br/>data/reports/]
    SaveReport --> OutputCheck
    
    OutputCheck{Output mode?}
    OutputCheck -->|JSON to file| SaveFile[Save to data/results/<br/>--output flag]
    OutputCheck -->|stdout| PrintStdout[Print JSON to stdout]
    OutputCheck -->|Batch| BatchSaveFile[Save aggregated JSON<br/>to data/results/]
    
    SaveFile --> End([End])
    PrintStdout --> End
    BatchSaveFile --> End
    
